<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 12:11:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>联阿援助团重申对阿富汗妇女和女童权利的承诺</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/unama-reiterates-its-commitment-to-rights-of-women-girls-in-afghanistan/articleshow/105879576.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105879576.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于阿富汗塔利班统治下的妇女和女童的基本人权继续遭到剥夺，联合国阿富汗援助团（联阿援助团）在世界人权日之际重申其对该国妇女和女童权利的承诺据卡马出版社报道。联阿援助团负责人罗扎·奥通巴耶娃表示，阿富汗是国际人权条约的签署国，维护人权对于阿富汗未来的福祉、和解与稳定至关重要。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 11:29:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/unama-reiterates-its-commitment-to-rights-of-women-girls-in-afghanistan/articleshow/105879576.cms</guid></item><item><title>从《巴黎协定》到 COP28，石油和天然气巨头如何试图影响全球气候议程</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/environment/global-warming/from-the-paris-agreement-to-cop28-how-oil-and-gas-giants-try-to-influence-the-global-climate-agenda/articleshow/105879327.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105879327.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;缔约方会议主席驳回了逐步淘汰化石燃料的呼吁，声称此类要求没有科学依据。然而，令人担忧的是，该会议已成为石油交易平台，参加化石燃料游说者数量创历史新高。石油巨头此前曾主张对公司的二氧化碳排放征收碳税，建议采取涉及全球实施和国际协议的两步走办法。由于需要国际协调，在全球范围内实施碳税具有挑战性，因为如果不是所有国家都参与，可能会发生碳泄漏。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 11:14:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/environment/global-warming/from-the-paris-agreement-to-cop28-how-oil-and-gas-giants-try-to-influence-the-global-climate-agenda/articleshow/105879327.cms</guid></item><item><title>人权组织在纪念国际人权日时表示，中国对异见采取强硬态度</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-is-hardening-against-dissent-rights-groups-say-as-they-mark-international-human-rights-day/articleshow/105879011.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105879011.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;卢丽娜的丈夫刘四方于2019年逃离中国，以逃避警方对异见人士的镇压。卢父子面临着诸多困难，包括被学校开除、被禁止出境等。他们不得不在中国申请离婚以绕过出境禁令。此案反映了北京对国内外异见人士的严厉镇压。人权组织认为，西方政府对中国施加的压力还不够，而习近平政权对国际压力的免疫力也越来越高。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 10:53:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-is-hardening-against-dissent-rights-groups-say-as-they-mark-international-human-rights-day/articleshow/105879011.cms</guid></item><item><title>斯里兰卡议会会议因法定人数不足而休会至周一</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/sri-lanka-parliament-session-adjourned-till-monday-due-to-lack-of-quorum/articleshow/105878896.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105878896.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;斯里兰卡议会会议因讨论增值税修订法案时缺乏法定人数而休会。反对党成员对缺乏征收增值税的物品清单提出抗议。国际货币基金组织董事会将于12月12日召开会议，批准发放第二批3.3亿美元的救助计划。财政部长表示，增值税上调将有助于国家收入增加1.2%，并将国家总收入目标提高到2024年占GDP的12.5%。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 10:45:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/sri-lanka-parliament-session-adjourned-till-monday-due-to-lack-of-quorum/articleshow/105878896.cms</guid></item><item><title>COP28主席警告“失败不是一种选择”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/cop28-head-warns-failure-is-not-an-option/articleshow/105879789.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105879789.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 11:41:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/cop28-head-warns-failure-is-not-an-option/articleshow/105879789.cms</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔表示，延长以色列与哈马斯停火协议的努力“仍在继续”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/qatar-says-efforts-to-renew-israel-hamas-truce-continuing/articleshow/105878174.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105878174.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;卡塔尔总理表示，尽管以色列持续轰炸，但确保加沙新停火的努力仍在继续。卡塔尔及其合作伙伴正在继续进行调解努力，并决心不放弃。然而，由于以色列的持续轰炸，取得成功的机会正在缩小。联合国秘书长还对安理会对冲突反应迟缓表示失望，他认为这损害了安理会的权威和信誉。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 09:58:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/qatar-says-efforts-to-renew-israel-hamas-truce-continuing/articleshow/105878174.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗和沙特阿拉伯就直航定期航班进行谈判 - ILNA</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-and-saudi-arabia-to-negotiate-on-direct-scheduled-flights-ilna/articleshow/105878325.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105878325.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊朗官员周日告诉伊朗国家通讯社ILNA，伊朗和沙特阿拉伯将于下周开始正式谈判，以恢复德黑兰和利雅得及其他城市之间的直飞定期航班。定期航班将是恢复这两个中东竞争对手之间关系的又一步。今年三月，中国斡旋达成一项协议，在多年的紧张局势之后恢复了外交关系，这种紧张局势威胁到整个地区的安全，并加剧了伊拉克、叙利亚和也门的冲突。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 10:09:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-and-saudi-arabia-to-negotiate-on-direct-scheduled-flights-ilna/articleshow/105878325.cms</guid></item><item><title>亚历克斯·琼斯 (Alex Jones) 是谁？他的 X 账户已被埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 恢复</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/who-is-alex-jones-the-conspiracy-theorist-whose-x-account-has-been-reinstated-by-elon-musk/articleshow/105878298.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105878298.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 10:14:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/who-is-alex-jones-the-conspiracy-theorist-whose-x-account-has-been-reinstated-by-elon-musk/articleshow/105878298.cms</guid></item><item><title>法国表示，其一艘军舰遭到来自也门方向的无人机袭击。两人均被击落</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/france-says-one-of-its-warships-was-targeted-by-drones-from-direction-of-yemen-both-were-shot-down/articleshow/105878161.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105878161.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;法国周日表示，其在红海的一艘军舰遭到来自也门的无人机袭击。两者都被拦截并击落。陆军部的一份简短声明没有说明是谁在周六晚上向法国海军护卫舰朗格多克号发射了无人机。据称，无人机从也门方向“径直袭击”了这艘船——一架接一架，相隔两个小时。据称，这艘军舰在距也门海岸荷台达红海港约 110 公里（70 英里）处摧毁了这两艘船。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 09:57:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/france-says-one-of-its-warships-was-targeted-by-drones-from-direction-of-yemen-both-were-shot-down/articleshow/105878161.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京竞选连任面临挑战</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/vladimir-putin-faces-challenges-amid-re-election-bid/articleshow/105876383.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105876383.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 10:00:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/vladimir-putin-faces-challenges-amid-re-election-bid/articleshow/105876383.cms</guid></item><item><title>世卫组织总干事：加沙战争对健康造成“灾难性”影响</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/gaza-war-having-catastrophic-health-impact-who-chief/articleshow/105878005.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105878005.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;世界卫生组织总干事谭德塞周日表示，以色列和哈马斯之间的战争正在对加沙地带的健康造成灾难性影响。联合国卫生机构总干事在世卫组织执行委员会特别会议开幕式上表示，“冲突对健康的影响是灾难性的”，卫生工作者在难以想象的条件下从事着不可能完成的工作，该会议旨在讨论巴勒斯坦领土的卫生状况。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 09:42:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/gaza-war-having-catastrophic-health-impact-who-chief/articleshow/105878005.cms</guid></item><item><title>走私者将移民带到偏远的亚利桑那州边境口岸，令美国特工不知所措</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/smugglers-are-bringing-migrants-to-a-remote-arizona-border-crossing-overwhelming-us-agents/articleshow/105875025.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105875025.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于来自塞内加尔、孟加拉国和中国等国家的移民涌入，美国政府无限期关闭了亚利桑那州卢克维尔过境点。关闭的目的是让海关和边境保护局官员腾出时间来协助运输和支持。然而，包括亚利桑那州民主党州长凯蒂·霍布斯在内的批评者认为，此举可能会损害贸易和旅游业。由于地处偏远且边境巡逻人员较少，卢克维尔地区已成为过境的热门地点。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 06:27:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/smugglers-are-bringing-migrants-to-a-remote-arizona-border-crossing-overwhelming-us-agents/articleshow/105875025.cms</guid></item><item><title>对于普京来说，赢得连任可能比解决俄罗斯面临的许多挑战更容易</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/for-putin-winning-reelection-could-be-easier-than-resolving-the-many-challenges-facing-russia/articleshow/105874295.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105874295.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 06:13:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/for-putin-winning-reelection-could-be-easier-than-resolving-the-many-challenges-facing-russia/articleshow/105874295.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国特别报告员谴责阿富汗罪行缺乏问责</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/un-special-rapporteur-condemns-lack-of-accountability-for-crimes-in-afghanistan/articleshow/105873813.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105873813.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国阿富汗问题特别报告员理查德·贝内特谴责对战争罪、危害人类罪和侵犯人权行为缺乏问责。在纽约举行的“追究阿富汗境内所犯罪行的责任”会议强调了对阿富汗侵犯人权和违反国际人道主义法的行为进行问责的重要性。国际过渡时期司法中心（ICTJ）呼吁成员国，特别是卷入冲突的国家，为本国公民立案。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 05:17:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/un-special-rapporteur-condemns-lack-of-accountability-for-crimes-in-afghanistan/articleshow/105873813.cms</guid></item><item><title>法新社：近200名罗兴亚人滞留在印尼海滩</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nearly-200-rohingya-stranded-on-indonesia-beach-afp/articleshow/105873254.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105873254.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;当地政府拒绝接收近 200 名罗兴亚难民，其中大部分是妇女和儿童，他们被困在印度尼西亚西部的海滩上。这些难民乘船抵达，加入了自 2015 年以来最大规模的罗兴亚人涌入行列。2017 年面临缅甸军方镇压的罗兴亚人已逃往孟加拉国，并试图通过危险的海上旅程前往马来西亚或印度尼西亚。船只停靠的亚齐省当地政府拒绝向难民提供基本需求。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 04:34:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nearly-200-rohingya-stranded-on-indonesia-beach-afp/articleshow/105873254.cms</guid></item><item><title>香港根据新规定举行首次立法会选举，民主派候选人被排除在外</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/hong-kong-holds-first-council-elections-under-new-rules-that-shut-out-pro-democracy-candidates/articleshow/105872830.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105872830.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;香港居民参加了区议会选举，这是自北京指导下的选举改革有效排除亲民主候选人以来的首次投票。由于规则的变化，包括取消直选席位，预计投票率将会降低。这次选举将衡量公众对新的“爱国者”制度的看法。 2021年修改了选举法，降低了公众投票能力，并增加了亲北京的立法者。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 03:58:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/hong-kong-holds-first-council-elections-under-new-rules-that-shut-out-pro-democracy-candidates/articleshow/105872830.cms</guid></item><item><title>恶劣天气席卷田纳西州，房屋受损，电力中断</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/homes-damaged-power-knocked-out-as-severe-weather-rakes-tennessee/articleshow/105870857.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105870857.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一场明显的龙卷风在田纳西州克拉克斯维尔造成了广泛的破坏，导致数千人断电，并引发了多次龙卷风警报。风暴掀翻了房屋的屋顶，掀翻了一辆拖拉机拖车，碎片散落在草坪上。尽管遭到破坏，但尚未确认有人受伤或失踪。美国国家气象局还报告称肯塔基州出现了明显的龙卷风，并计划对受影响地区进行调查。目前，田纳西州约有 85,000 个电力客户断电。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 01:23:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/homes-damaged-power-knocked-out-as-severe-weather-rakes-tennessee/articleshow/105870857.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国否决联合国休战推动后，以色列袭击加沙北部和南部</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/after-us-vetoes-un-truce-push-israel-hits-north-south-gaza/articleshow/105868182.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105868182.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列继续对加沙地带北部和南部进行空袭和炮击。联合国秘书长安东尼奥·古特雷斯援引《联合国宪章》第99条警告加沙将发生“人道主义灾难”。美国否决了联合国立即停火的决议，称这将允许哈马斯继续统治加沙。一名被哈马斯武装分子扣为人质的以色列男子在救援任务中死亡。加沙死亡人数已超过17,400人，超过46,000人受伤。在约旦河西岸，两名巴勒斯坦人被以色列军队杀害。</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Dec 2023 20:32:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/after-us-vetoes-un-truce-push-israel-hits-north-south-gaza/articleshow/105868182.cms</guid></item><item><title>易卜拉欣·莱西会见弗拉基米尔·普京，称与俄罗斯的合作对伊朗的周边政策很重要</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/ebrahim-raisi-meets-vladimir-putin-calls-cooperation-with-russia-important-in-irans-neighbourhood-policy/articleshow/105868162.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105868162.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊朗总统易卜拉欣·莱西在莫斯科会见俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京，讨论伊朗与俄罗斯之间不断发展的关系。莱西强调了与俄罗斯合作符合伊朗周边政策的重要性，并强调了能源、农业和知识型公司等领域的合作。普京赞扬俄罗斯商人在伊朗贸易展览会上受到的热烈接待以及两国贸易的增长。他们讨论了地区问题，包括巴勒斯坦和加沙局势。莱西批评以色列的行为是种族灭绝，并指责西方支持它。</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Dec 2023 20:23:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/ebrahim-raisi-meets-vladimir-putin-calls-cooperation-with-russia-important-in-irans-neighbourhood-policy/articleshow/105868162.cms</guid></item><item><title>苏纳克如何从卢旺达计划批评者转变为将未来押在该计划上</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/how-sunak-went-from-rwanda-plan-critic-to-staking-future-on-it/articleshow/105868080.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105868080.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 2022 年，英国财政大臣里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 私下对将寻求庇护者驱逐到卢旺达的严厉新移民政策表示担忧。现在，作为总理，他通过了卢旺达的计划来消除民调赤字。然而，该计划面临挑战，英国法院裁定其非法，高级部长离开内阁。苏纳克现在正试图平息他所在政党的叛乱，因为他面临着实施该政策的投票。</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Dec 2023 19:46:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/how-sunak-went-from-rwanda-plan-critic-to-staking-future-on-it/articleshow/105868080.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>